<div class="container">
<h1 class="c-headingA01">方針等</h1>
</div>
</div>
<div class="c-section-A01">
<div class="container">
<div class="row-gutter-0px medium-row-gutter-0px large-row-gutter-0px">
<div class="col-12of12 medium-col-6of12 large-col-4of12 margin-vert-10px medium-margin-vert-20px">
<div class="c-card-A1 expanded">
<div class="c-card-A01__thumb"><a href="/company/policy/solicitation/"><img class="img-responsive expanded" src="/company/policy/images/img_1.jpg" alt="" width="334" height="187" /></a></div>
<div class="c-card-A01__content">
<h3 class="p-movie-list-item__heading margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px"><a href="/company/policy/solicitation/">勧誘方針</a></h3>
<div class="c-card-A01__body">
<p class="c-card-A01__desc-text margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px">証券投資信託の直接募集・解約等は行っておりませんが、当社の「金融商品の販売等に係る勧誘方針」を掲載しています。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-12of12 medium-col-6of12 large-col-4of12 margin-vert-10px medium-margin-vert-20px">
<div class="c-card-A1 expanded">
<div class="c-card-A01__thumb"><a href="/company/policy/stewardship/" title="日本版スチュワードシップ・コード"><img class="img-responsive expanded" src="/company/policy/images/img_2.jpg" alt="" width="334" height="187" /></a></div>
<div class="c-card-A01__content">
<h3 class="p-movie-list-item__heading margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px"><a href="/company/policy/stewardship/">日本版スチュワードシップ・コード</a></h3>
<div class="c-card-A01__body">
<p class="c-card-A01__desc-text margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px"><span>日本版スチュワードシップ・コードに対する当社方針を公表しています。</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-12of12 medium-col-6of12 large-col-4of12 margin-vert-10px medium-margin-vert-20px">
<div class="c-card-A1 expanded">
<div class="c-card-A01__thumb"><a href="/company/policy/voting/"><img class="img-responsive expanded" src="/company/policy/images/img_3.jpg" alt="" width="334" height="187" /></a></div>
<div class="c-card-A01__content">
<h3 class="p-movie-list-item__heading margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px"><a href="/company/policy/voting/">議決権行使</a></h3>
<div class="c-card-A01__body">
<p class="c-card-A01__desc-text margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px">議決権行使に関する基本的な考え方、議決権行使結果等を公表しています。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-12of12 medium-col-6of12 large-col-4of12 margin-vert-10px medium-margin-vert-20px">
<div class="c-card-A1 expanded">
<div class="c-card-A01__thumb"><a href="/company/policy/fiduciary/"><img class="img-responsive expanded" src="/company/policy/images/img_4.jpg" alt="" width="334" height="187" /></a></div>
<div class="c-card-A01__content">
<h3 class="p-movie-list-item__heading margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px"><a href="/company/policy/fiduciary/">フィデューシャリー・デューティーへの取り組み</a></h3>
<div class="c-card-A01__body">
<p class="c-card-A01__desc-text margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px">当社のフィデューシャリー・デューティーへの取り組みを公表しています。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-12of12 medium-col-6of12 large-col-4of12 margin-vert-10px medium-margin-vert-20px">
<div class="c-card-A1 expanded">
<div class="c-card-A01__thumb"><a href="/company/policy/coi/"><img class="img-responsive expanded" src="/company/policy/images/img_5.jpg" alt="" width="334" height="187" /></a></div>
<div class="c-card-A01__content">
<h3 class="p-movie-list-item__heading margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px"><a href="/company/policy/coi/">利益相反管理方針（概要）</a></h3>
<div class="c-card-A01__body">
<p class="c-card-A01__desc-text margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px">当社の利益相反管理方針（概要）を公表しています。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-12of12 medium-col-6of12 large-col-4of12 margin-vert-10px medium-margin-vert-20px">
<div class="c-card-A1 expanded">
<div class="c-card-A01__thumb"><a href="/company/policy/declaration/index.html"><img class="img-responsive expanded" src="/company/policy/images/.jpg" alt="" width="334" height="187" /></a></div>
<div class="c-card-A01__content">
<h3 class="p-movie-list-item__heading margin-horizon-10px medium-margin-horizon-30px margin-left-0px"><a href="/company/policy/declaration/index.html">各種宣言・表明等</a></h3>
<div class="c-card-A01__body">
<p>各種の宣言や表明等を掲載しています。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
